snippet.title: Psikyo Shooting Stars Alpha & Bravo - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch) (EU - English)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/psikyo-shooting-stars/

One legendary company. Two fiery collections. Twelve exhilarating arcade hits. Brace yourself for intense white-knuckle action with Psikyo Shooting Stars Alpha & Bravo! Experience the thrilling titles that defined the arcade shooter genre as we know it!

Coming to Nintendo Switch in 2020.
